{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><i>Welcome to Berzerk Flashback*, an anthology of pretty much all the Flash games we still have the source code for.</i></h2><br>You can now play your favorite Berzerk time wasters from a decade ago, Berzerk Ball, Sands of the Coliseum, Frantic Frigates, Gunbot, you name it! All safe from the grasp of whoever is trying to take Flash games away from us.<br><br>We freed all the games from their microtransactions and ads, only pure, innocent games here, well, as innocent as games about war, gladiators, all around violence and eating animal proteins can be.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1505700/extras/BZA_HeaderTitle_02.gif?t=1667221240\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Mechanical commando<br></li><li> Hero's Arms<br></li><li> Swordless Ninja<br></li><li> Trap Master<br></li><li> Mechanical Commando 2<br></li><li> Homerun in Berzerk Land<br></li><li> The Breach<br></li><li> Gunbot<br></li><li> Frantic Frigates<br></li><li> Delivery Man<br></li><li> Rocket Santa<br></li><li> Nuclear Justice 2084<br></li><li> Sands of the Coliseum<br></li><li> Rocket Santa 2<br></li><li> Berzerk Ball 2<br></li><li> The Peacekeeper<br></li><li> BattleCry<br></li><li> Sky Quest</li></ul><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1505700/extras/BZA_HeaderTitle_03.gif?t=1667221240\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Also included is a bunch of sideprojects and unreleased lolities, like I dunno, the Just Shapes &amp; Beats prototype and Frantic Frigates 2.</li></ul><br><br>Hope these little time capsules of a simpler time bring you as much joy as they did back then!<br><br><br><br>*Get it... Flashback... because like... it's <strong>flash</strong> games... that we're bringing <strong>back</strong>... <i>f\u00a0l\u00a0a\u00a0s\u00a0h\u00a0b\u00a0a\u00a0c\u00a0k</i>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Gotta start somewher